            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1690876681487-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1690876681487-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>brown</strong> <strong>onion[s]</strong>, then peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>free range</strong> <strong>chicken thighs</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>ground smoked paprika </strong>and <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>smoky chicken thighs</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1690876686125-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1690876686125-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1690876686125-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1690876686125-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1690876686125-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid)  with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>smoky chicken thighs</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until lightly charred</p><p>Transfer the<strong> charred chicken</strong> to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) and put the tray[s] in the oven for 10 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!), reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-2-1690876703089-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-2-1690876703089-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-2-1690876703089-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-2-1690876703089-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-2-1690876703089-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat with a little drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 2-3 min until starting to soften</p><p>Whilst the onion is softening, slice half of your <strong>green chilli[es]</strong> into rounds and set aside for garnish</p><p>Finely chop the <strong>remaining green chilli[es]</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-1690876708509-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-1690876708509-x400.jpg",
