            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [600ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Once the onion has slightly softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and<strong> chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>with your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>turmeric </strong>and <strong>curry powder</strong> to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook for 1 min until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1690876712485-x200.jpg",
