          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1690876712485-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>diced carrot</strong> and cook<strong> </strong>for 2-3 min or until slightly softened</p><p>Add the <strong>diced pepper</strong>, <strong>white long grain rice </strong>and <strong>bay leaf[ves]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>to the pan with the <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>stock </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1690876716752-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1690876716752-x400.jpg",
