            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-copy-1690876720142-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoky free range chicken thighs </strong>over the <strong>West African-style spicy rice</strong>, discard the <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chilli rounds</strong></p><p>Drizzle any <strong>remaining juices </strong>from the chicken over the rice</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
